Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Occupy the middle of this year

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE and PRD Commercial have been appointed as the Exclusive Marketing Agents to offer the prestigious new Rise Commercial Estate located at 55 Leland St, Penrith.

Strategically located in the heart of the Penrith Industrial Precinct, this complex is an integral part of the Western Sydney growth corridor. Just 6 minutes* to the Penrith CBD, 8 minutes* to the M4 Motorway and only 27 minutes* to the new Western Sydney Airport.

The property features the following:
- Last available unit
- 141sqm (approx.) industrial warehouse
- Architecturally designed complex
- Secure concrete panel construction
- High clearance warehouse
- Clearspan warehouse floor
- Mezzanine area ideal for office or storage
- Internal amenities
- Parking allocated to each unit

Contact the team for an Information Memorandum and further details.

Note: All building and land areas quoted are approximate; prospective purchasers and tenants must make their own enquiries. All sale prices and asking rentals DO NOT include GST.
